{"tid":528661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"通緝犯愛演戲變知名演員 逃亡13年被認出","createTime":"2018-01-14T05:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T06:29:47.000Z","uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fd614e946a1bf8867f891942a5eaee0909e2a935","tid":528661,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T05:34:19.000Z","msg":"戲如人生，還是人生如戲？黑龍江齊齊哈爾一名男子，13年前因涉及一宗盜竊及襲警案，潛逃到深圳後隱姓埋名，更在朋友介紹下做了演員，演出30多部電視劇，經常在電視螢幕出鏡的他，竟一直並未被人發現。<br />\n<br />\n直至他因演出講述國共內戰間諜鬥法的電視劇《潛伏》而走紅，才被警員揭發身份而落網，判監10年。<br />\n<br />\n這名身世充滿傳的演員名叫吉世光，1998年因生活所迫，聯同另外兩人搶劫刑警楊琳，還襲擊他的妻子。當時，楊琳的前胸、後背被連刺兩刀，導致脊柱神經斷裂重傷。<br />\n<br />\n那年，吉世光才26歲，事後由齊齊哈爾潛逃到深圳，因為他學過表演，唱歌，所以就在深圳當上了歌手和主持人。<br />\n<br />\n之後他改名叫「張國鋒」，更在朋友介紹下到浙江省東陽市橫店當起「咖喱啡」臨時演員。吉世光曾演出30多部戲，包括多部受歡迎電視劇，如《武則天秘史》、《倚天屠龍記》、《新還珠格格》等。<br />\n<br />\n吉世光漸漸地累積了一些演技，2008年被電視劇《潛伏》的導演睇中，給了他戲份頗重的角色。<br />\n<br />\n他甚至因為這部戲，還被選為最佳男配角。但成也蕭何、敗也蕭何，吉世光因為這部戲走紅，卻被齊齊哈爾一名老刑警從從劇集中認了出來，經過多方的仔細辨認，警方確定這個人就是潛逃多年的通緝犯吉世光。<br />\n<br />\n2011年12月7日，警方的專案小組經過調查，最終鎖定吉世光的行蹤，隨即展開部署埋伏，最終在浙江金華市將39歲的吉世光拘捕。<br />\n事實上，直到落網時，吉世光手中仍握有不少片約，他在一部新攝製的電視劇《少林猛虎》中扮演和尚，該劇已經拍了30場。<br />\n<br />\n警方亦指，吉世光被逮捕後神情輕鬆，還要求警方「給我多帶點衣服」、「我要吃火腿湯，我要吃方便麵，我要喝飲料」，警方也說他睡覺的呼嚕聲特別大響。<br />\n<br />\n而內地網友評論吉世光的故事，紛紛說：「逃亡的人生天天都在演戲，NG一次就完蛋了。」、「人生就是一場戲。」、「大隱隱於電視。」<br />\n<br />\n微博<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180114/20273855\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F20273855&d=29r2hRuK8n6t4NwmtKp%2FnL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=c77e338f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F20273855&h=5347d8bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180114/20273855</a>"},{"pid":"d4186e2db980f49ce30ec45ed21fe493a50dab65","tid":528661,"uid":28765,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20170207/df86ee86777546368793f9f9dd82bbb5_th.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.mp.itc.cn%2Fupload%2F20170207%2Fdf86ee86777546368793f9f9dd82bbb5_th.jpeg&h=726c9f34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTSTZSQkL9CV-e4gOZFWaETk8wkixXw90pFBW7LSbw-tU7nVaUq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcTSTZSQkL9CV-e4gOZFWaETk8wkixXw90pFBW7LSbw-tU7nVaUq&h=86fc0b86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/apis/web/viaphoto2/63440/3061708\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fapis%2Fweb%2Fviaphoto2%2F63440%2F3061708&h=68a3485d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6c619c351cc79d59548a56d6239f2bff8a0c664","tid":528661,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T05:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd7171890e5c05cb2b2434be545b2df792eb0df","tid":528661,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:27:35.000Z","msg":"咁都認到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634c6f6620f818bb8c1db5648e7807f71d5dac3d","tid":528661,"uid":20286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}